data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS! This stunning MOVE IN ready, two-story SMART home is on a large lot in a desirable neighborhood. From the open-concept kitchen and living space to the large backyard, there is plenty of room for the whole family to enjoy. This home also features a MAYTAG water filtration system that supplies filtered soft water throughout the house, and shallow well water for irrigation so you can save money on your water bill! NO CDD and an easy drive to NAS JAX! Sellers will pay up to 2% towards Buyers closing cost.
